.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, punk, jazz, trance
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, western, zombie
1. the fan of trance is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
2. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
3. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
6. the fan of trance is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre          | jazz | trance   | salsa   | punk    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | zombie | disaster | western |

