.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, cola, water
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, russian, thai, turkish
1. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the turkish is between the person drinking water and the thai##2
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate | fanta | water | cola |
| Nationality   | thai        | turkish     | japanese       | russian   |

