.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz, salsa
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, tennis, ice-hockey, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is tennis is the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of ambient is between the fan of hip-hop and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
3. the person who's sport is cricket is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5
5. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
6. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient  | jazz  | salsa   |
| Sport           | weightlifting  | cricket | ice-hockey | tennis |

