.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, american, egyptian, russian
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, librarian, mechanic, scientist
1. the librarian is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the russian is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the russian is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
4. the american is on the left of the russian##1
5. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american     | russian | egyptian     | malaysian   |
| Job    | scientist | librarian  | mechanic | designer |

