2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
5. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
6. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | milk   | cola |
| Music-Genre       | classical       | folk   | blues | pop |

