.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, journalist, police-officer, bartender
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, surfing, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the police-officer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
4. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
5. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Job   | journalist | police-officer       | firefighter   | bartender        |
| Sport      | surfing  | weightlifting | soccer | water-polo |

