.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, fishing, sudoku
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, green, lilac, pink
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
2. the person who likes lilac is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lilac##5
5. the person who likes green is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
6. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | board-games | drawing   | fishing | sudoku     |
| Color   | green     | white | lilac  | pink |

