.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, horror, spy
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, quad-bike, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person watching animation movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
6. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | horror        | spy        | epic |
| Transport         | quad-bike  | motorbike | airplane | bus |

