2. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | disaster | documentary | thriller |
| Hobby   | video-games | collecting | photography   | filmmaking  |

