2. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
5. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | puzzles  | singing      | gardening |
| Game     | billiard    | go | canasta | chess   |

