.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, sunflower, zinnia, begonia
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, gospel, hip-hop
1. the person who growszinnia is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
6. the person who growszinnia is between the person who growsiris and the fan of electronic##2
7. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsiris##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Flower      | iris   | zinnia  | sunflower      | begonia       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | electronic | classical |

