There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, french, nigerian, turkish
1. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
3. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
4. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
5. the egyptian is on the left of the french##1
6. the person watching sports movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Movie-Genre      | animation     | time-travel | sports     | epic |
| Nationality   | nigerian | turkish  | egyptian | french        |

