.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, hamster, mouse
House: craftsman, townhouse, victorian, colonial
1. the owner of the bird is between the townhouse house and the owner of the goldfish##2
2. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
3. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
4. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet         | hamster   | mouse   | bird       | goldfish   |
| House   | victorian | townhouse | craftsman | colonial |

