.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapes, strawberry, watermelon
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, pall-mall, aristoff, cain
1. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##5
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the cain-smoker##5
6. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating watermelon and the bluemaster-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | grapes     | watermelon | asparagus | strawberry |
| Cigar   | aristoff | cain | pall-mall      | bluemaster        |

 